Event::IO
=========

The Event::IO modules are some modules that simplify use of the excellent
Event module.

Event::IO::Record provides buffered I/O.

Event::IO::Server provides a simple server framework.

INSTALLATION

To install this module type the following:

   perl Build.PL
   ./Build
   ./Build test
   ./Build install

DEPENDENCIES

This module requires the Event module.

